data.text:
Sarawak is also known as Bumi Kenyalang ('Land of the Hornbills') . Sarawak is on of two Malaysian states located in the island of Borneo . It is the largest state in Malaysia .

The capital of Sarawak is Kuching . Sarawak has more than 40 sub-ethnic groups which include Dayak Iban , Chinese , Malay , Melanau , Dayak Bidayuh , Dayak Saloka & Lara , Indian , Eurasian , Javanese , Bugis , Bisaya , Kedayan and Dayak Orang Ulu . Sarawak's current Yang di-Pertua Negeri is Abang Muhammad Salahuddin and its current Menteri Besar is Abdul Taib Muhammad .
